  "instructions": [
    "cook papelon according to package instructions.",
    "grill chicken until cooked through.",
    "dice onion and garlic, then saut\u00159 in olive oil until softened.",
    "add tomato paste, stirring constantly, and cook for 1 minute.",
    "add ground chicken, breaking it up with a spoon, and cook until no longer pink.",
    "stir in bechamel sauce, parmesan cheese, and a pinch of salt and pepper.",
    "combine cooked papelon, chicken mixture, and chopped parsley in a baking dish.",
    "top with crumbled feta cheese and a sprinkle of paprika.",
    "bake at 375\u00134f for 20-25 minutes, or until golden brown and bubbly."
